The Maratha Empire wasn't always a Confederacy, during it's early stages it was governed directly by the 'Chhatrapati' (Emperor) so it could be consideredas an empire, but during it's later stages the 'Chhatrapati' became more of a titular head instead of a full governing position, instead the 'Peshwa'(Prime Minister) took power and controlled the Empire and other factions seized power during that time so that would make it a 'Confederacy' instead of an Empire.
